About Me
Started from a basic hello world program in C++ to developing web apps from scratch, I really came a long way. After graduating from Institute of Technology and Science, I got placed in TCS. Training period helped me to experience latest technologies like Machine Learning and Deep Learning which made me fell in love with Python projects. But on the other side I always wanted to be one of the best UI developers which made me learn ReactJS and full stack by my own. You can find some of the projects under Projects page.
